- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and language modeling using deep neural networks.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and audio data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a likely category as the paper proposes a strategy to select data for unsupervised adaptation of DNN models.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with deep neural networks and their application in speech recognition.
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is a possible category as the paper deals with processing of audio signals for speech recognition.
